This tool, together with timeplot (http://github.com/jkff/timeplot), aims to make tasks of visualizing/analyzing system behavior based on log files into shell one-liners.

See presentation: http://www.slideshare.net/jkff/two-visualization-tools

Also see current documentation page: http://www.haskell.org/haskellwiki/Splot

Also see hackage package: http://hackage.haskell.org/package/splot